<h1>要</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#000099;">yào</span><span class=alesi>(yao4)</span> , <span style="color:#990000;">yāo</span><span class=alesi>(yao1)</span> , <span style="color:#009900;">yǎo</span><span class=alesi>(yao3)</span> <span class=lesi>// pronunciations of 要 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 要</h2><div class=abo>
<p><b>Unihan definition:</b> <a href="/dictionary/necessary" style="color:black;">necessary</a>, <a href="/dictionary/essential" style="color:black;">essential</a>; <a href="/dictionary/necessity" style="color:black;">necessity</a></p><p><b>Number of strokes:</b> 9<br><small>Examples of other characters consisting of 9 strokes: <a href="/character/是" title="shi4: indeed, yes, right; to be; demonstrative pronoun, this, that">是</a>, <a href="/character/说" title="shuo1: speak, say, talk; scold, upbraid">说</a>, <a href="/character/种" title="zhong3: seed; race, breed; to plant">种</a>, <a href="/character/面" title="mian4: face; surface; plane; side, dimension">面</a>, <a href="/character/看" title="kan4: look, see; examine, scrutinize">看</a>, <a href="/character/前" title="qian2: in front, forward; preceding">前</a>, <a href="/character/点" title="dian3: dot, speck, spot; point, degree">点</a>, <a href="/character/将" title="jiang1: will, going to, future; general">将</a>, <a href="/character/很" title="hen3: very, quite, much">很</a>, <a href="/character/重" title="zhong4: heavy, weighty; double">重</a></small></p><p><b>Radical:</b> <a href="/character/襾" title="Kangxi radical 146">襾</a>&nbsp;146.3</p><p><b>HSK level:</b> 2 <br><small>Other HSK 2 characters: <a href="/character/就" title="jiu4: just, simply; to come, go to; to approach, near">就</a>, <a href="/character/以" title="yi3: by means of; thereby, therefore; consider as; in order to">以</a>, <a href="/character/到" title="dao4: go to, arrive, been to">到</a>, <a href="/character/可" title="ke3: may, can, -able; possibly">可</a>, <a href="/character/也" title="ye3: also; classical final particle of strong affirmation or identity">也</a>, <a href="/character/为" title="wei4: do, handle, govern, act; be">为</a>, <a href="/character/得" title="de2: obtain, get, gain, acquire">得</a>, <a href="/character/着" title="zhe: make move, take action">着</a>, <a href="/character/过" title="guo4: pass, pass through, go across">过</a>, <a href="/character